nodes.title: Removed a debug broadcast I forgot to remove
Fixed sieges not ending as well as a formatting issue
Allow more specific entity movement customization
Fix ClassCastException when loading Craft type
Made ascend/cruise/descend signs auto update when one of them is changed
Fixed localisation strings to follow the function - identifier format
Header of Region Damaged sign has been localised
Fixed entity (player) movement and a few typos
Change remote signs to function with multiple remoted signs of the same label
Make it so cruise-on-pilot crafts can optionally play a sound when piloted.
Fixed grammar in rotation error message
Some additions you may be interested in
Support for newer mc versions (basic support)
Convert dynamicFlyBlock to a taggable set of materials
[1.13+] Do not take BlockState snapshots when using Paper or its forks.
Clean up english lang file and RotationTask
Make Status: signs display multi-flyblock counts
Do not change crew signs if the event has been cancelled.
Possibly fixed a few NPEs regarding null piloted crafts
Clean up unused imports in ManOverboardCommand
Add optimizations from 1.10 to 1.11 and 1.12 IWorldHandler.
Setup continuous integration using GitHub Actions
Fixed helm signs to work when near a craft rather than within the hitbox
Fixed crafts affected by gravity not dropping
Remove bypassing of Spigot's safety checks on removing tile entities
Gson for reading repair sign text
